better clipboard interactions
    replace to eol with clipboard
    \c<motion> -> clipboard
    
    update mappings for \cv, \cf, \cd to target register
        -> function + <register>

improvements to quote, quote full lines, removing quotes
    use surround where possible
    motions for comma/quoting mappings
        https://stackoverflow.com/questions/42438795/vim-create-custom-command-that-takes-a-movement

better support in terminal (linux),  F1 to F4 doesn't work (mac ok)
    See :help xterm-function-keys and :help xterm-modifier-keys

